## ⚠️ CRITICAL Font and Text Colors

**NEVER use gray or light colors for fonts or text elements!**

### Font Color Requirements

- **All text MUST use dark colors**: `#1a1a1a` (black) or `#2c3e50` (dark blue-gray)
- **Forbidden colors**: `#888`, `#aaa`, `#ccc`, `#ddd`, `#eee`, `#f0f0f0`, or any light gray
- **Title text**: `#1a1a1a` with `fontWeight: "bold"`
- **Axis labels**: `#1a1a1a` (black)
- **Legend text**: `#1a1a1a` (black)
- **Tooltip text**: `#1a1a1a` (black) on light background
- **Data labels**: `#1a1a1a` (black) or contrasting color based on background

### Plot Element Colors

- **Axis lines**: `#2c3e50` (dark blue-gray) or `#34495e` (darker blue-gray) - NOT light gray
- **Grid lines**: `#ecf0f1` (very light gray) is acceptable for subtle grid, but prefer `rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.1)` (dark blue-gray with opacity)
- **Background**: White or very light neutral - avoid gray backgrounds
- **Borders**: `#2c3e50` or darker - never light gray

### Examples

```python
# ✅ CORRECT - Dark font colors
"title": {"textStyle": {"color": "#1a1a1a", "fontWeight": "bold"}}
"xAxis": {"axisLabel": {"color": "#1a1a1a"}}
"yAxis": {"axisLabel": {"color": "#1a1a1a"}}
"legend": {"textStyle": {"color": "#1a1a1a"}}

# ❌ WRONG - Light/gray font colors
"title": {"textStyle": {"color": "#888"}}  # Too light!
"xAxis": {"axisLabel": {"color": "#ccc"}}  # Too light!
```

